        priority 99
        virtual_ipaddress_excluded {
                192.168.1.180
        }
        track_interface {
                enp0s3 weight -2
        }
        track_script {
                chk_haproxy
                chk_lb
        }
}
```

*start and verify on patroni-1 node.*

```shell
systemctl start keepalived

ip addr show enp0s3
```

